parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause loss of power steering, overheating, and battery drain, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Engine failure can cause loss of power, stalling, and overheating, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the check engine light comes on
and the engine makes a knocking or slapping noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially harm occupants.
symptoms: smoke comes from the air vents
and there is a smell of fuel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Head gasket failure can cause oil leaks, engine damage, and overheating, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil leaks from the head gasket
and the check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag light to stay on, the horn to be inoperable, and the cruise control to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver without critical safety features.
symptoms: the airbag may not deploy in an accident
or the airbag may deploy unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause injuries and accidents, while the failure of airbags to deploy in an accident can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: airbags fail to deploy in an accident
bruising and facial abrasions from airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering wheel can cause loss of control, leading to accidents and injuries.
Transmission failure can cause loss of power, loss of control, and accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: the transmission fails to shift into gear
the transmission shifts into neutral while driving
the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise
the transmission fails to respond to driver input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping or hesitation can cause loss of power, loss of control, and accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: the transmission fails to shift into gear
the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise
